# Red Thread Deployment Guide
1. Install dependencies: `pip install -r ../code/requirements.txt`
2. Run the backend server: `python app.py`
3. The server will start on `http://127.0.0.1:5000`.
4. Open `frontend/index.html` in your browser (preferably using VS Code Live Server) to view the website.